---
title: Seasoned Pork Schnitzels with Roast Veggie Toss & Garlic-Parsley Yoghurt
description: It’s schnitty night, tonight! Coat pork in our classic panko mix for a crispy golden result. Then, to amp up the flavour,
serve it with the best herby yoghurt around town. No need to head out for a meal like this.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
